headline: Strength in Advanced Technology Unit Drives Nordson: Can the Momentum Sustain?
summary: NDSN's Advanced Technology sales rose 8% in the first nine months of 2025, driving margin gains and a bullish full-year outlook.

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock on Our Buy List and 2 We Turn Down
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
